<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/8 via-base-100 to-secondary/5 py-24 md:py-32 px-6" aria-label="Úvod">
	<!-- Decorative background circles -->
	<div class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-primary/5 blur-3xl pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
	<div class="absolute -bottom-16 -left-16 w-64 h-64 rounded-full bg-secondary/5 blur-3xl pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

	<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">
		<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary bg-clip-text text-transparent leading-tight">
			Hypotéka na rovinu
		</h1>
		<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-base-content/70 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
			Žádný finanční poradce, žádné provize, žádné reklamy.
			Jen férové kalkulačky a srozumitelné vysvětlení, jak to celé funguje.
		</p>

		<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6 mb-12">
			<a href="/kalkulacky/najem-vs-vlastni" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg text-lg px-10 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-300 no-underline">
				Spočítej si to
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-1" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
					<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
				</svg>
			</a>
			<a href="/clanky" class="btn btn-ghost text-base-content/70 no-underline">
				Nebo si nejdřív přečti, jak to funguje
			</a>
		</div>

		<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-4 bg-base-100/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl shadow-lg px-8 py-5 border border-base-200">
			<span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold bg-gradient-to-r from-error to-warning bg-clip-text text-transparent leading-none">
				13,3&times;
			</span>
			<span class="text-base text-base-content/60 text-left">
				ročních platů stojí<br />průměrný byt v&nbsp;Česku
			</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
